Title: ICT Management and Leadership Conference 2023
Description: Technology is vital for every Australian school. The rich integration of different technologies is needed to ensure a seamless experience for all users. ICT education professionals know the value of understanding the latest opportunities, the imminent threats and the importance of continuous learning. It is time to examine and reflect on how the systems in schools are becoming unified, seamless and intelligent. This Conference brings ICT and education professionals together for a better tomorrow.
